Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.83,0:00:14.89,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\blur1\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:15.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:19.31,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:23.00,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:26.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:30.38,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:33.55,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:36.68,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:40.14,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:44.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:48.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:51.11,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:54.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:00:59.33,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:02.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:11.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:14.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.93,0:01:19.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:23.84,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HFCFFFE&\b1\pos(496.495,226.833)}The Monstrous Mantis Man
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.79,0:01:32.79,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\}Central Earthquake\NResearch Facility
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Central Earthquake\NResearch Facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.49,0:01:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm Chikako Amemiya of the Academic\NSociety for Earthquake Prediction.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.14,0:01:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we have all the\Nlatest equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes,\Nit's all utterly cutting-edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.94,0:02:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the newspapers\Nwere interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me,\Nbut might I ask who's calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A power outage?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there? The security guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Did a fuse blow out somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:02:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Mr. Guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Must've been an earthquake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... it scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had a lot of them\Nlately, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We might have a\Nbig one coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you put that\Nas a 5.0 magnitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnitude refers to the energy\Nemitted at the quake's epicenter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What we feel in each location is\Nmeasured in terms of seismic intensity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess even you mix them\Nup, Mr. Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So the intensity is lower as you\Nmove away from the epicenter...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I never realized that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So by creating a distribution plot\Nof seismic intensity readings,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and tracing back to\Nwhere it's the strongest,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:04:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you can learn the\Nlocation of the epicenter,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and that tells\Nyou the magnitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi is the one who taught\Nyou about epicenters, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least we know that catfish have\Nnothing to do with earthquakes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The usual, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of earthquakes...\Nremember Chikako Amemiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a childhood friend of\Nyours, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A sweet girl from my hometown,\Nthree years older than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe she's become a\Nrespected seismologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you bring her up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. She's gone missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, these aren't human cells!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They're insect cells!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like part of a spine\Nfrom a serrated insect leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But it would have to\Nbe one big insect...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What would something\Nlike that be doing on
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the floor of an earthquake\Nresearch center?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You picked it up because you\Nthought it was suspicious, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like there's a clue in the link\Nbetween that insect leg and this map.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of symbols\Nand numbers written on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a series of recent\Nearthquakes and their epicenter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we supposed\Nto learn from that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it strange to have\Nearthquakes occurring
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,on the outskirts of\Na city like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they are weak ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been seven\Nalready this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that is strange, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one\Nconclusion we can come to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the ones behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:01.26,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,It's considerably irradiated...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.41,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:06.32,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,I bet they're detonating small\Nnuclear payloads underground
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.11,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,and disguising them\Nas earthquakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:10.25,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They're tests!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They've done seven tests so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and the scale is\Ngradually increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They're plotting to\Nengineer a major earthquake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Chikako?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your help with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've found the main base of the people\Ntrying to engineer an earthquake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... come quickly. Alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The location is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Chikako!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd come.\NThank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain why I\Ninvited you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, we need to stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Show me the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside that hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Chikako!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo, you're helpless now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way out of that hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up...\Nyou have only two minutes to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.28,0:09:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you\Ncan reach this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to finish the\Nmodifications on scum like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Better to rid ourselves\Nof you entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:10:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And this bomb will be\Nthe perfect way to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just ninety seconds left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:20.72,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,I can't give in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:22.65,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,I'll struggle to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.57,0:10:52.96,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,If I die here, Shocker will be free\Nto cause a major earthquake in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:02.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When wind spins the turbine in\Ncyborg Hongo Takeshi's belt,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:05.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he transforms into\Nthe Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you survive that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind from the explosion\Ntriggered my belt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Give Chikako to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.33,0:11:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back or I'll kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Find him quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:42.39,Bumper Episode 2-13,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\pos(355,520)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You must retrieve that\Nwoman at all costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The success of Operation:\NArtificial Earthquake
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,depends on the aid of\Nthat earthquake expert!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:13:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Find her,\Nno matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi's late today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.87,0:13:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd normally be here by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be caught up\Nin his research again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something\Nyou're worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.16,0:13:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Shiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just outside... a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you've been\Nwatching too much TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I really saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A giant mantis monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.69,0:13:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She's waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor Chikako.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:14:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Chikako was just great at tag.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The neighborhood kids would\Nrun, but she'd always catch us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You played tag, Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have been\Nan adorable child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But now it's Shocker that's\Nchasing the both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.10,0:14:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me...\Nwill they come back to get her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to do\Nsomething, and fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Chikako. Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,An earthquake...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A major earthquake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,An earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Egg...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mantis egg...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker... at
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,4:00 PM...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Chikako! Chikako!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awake at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi's apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Chikako...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you explain what you\Nwere saying just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A major earthquake\Nand a mantis egg...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what\Nyou're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,4:00 PM... was that today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Chikako isn't even my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:47.04,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,I'm a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:51.95,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Shocker modified my body,\Ngiving me strength beyond my control...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:15:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Return her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Return the woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, get to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish preparations for Operation:\NArtificial Earthquake at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've calculated\Nthe nuclear energy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,needed based on\Ndetonation sites,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,crust vibrations, and necessary\Nmagnitude, and finished the placement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to destroy a city,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,we must target locations in which\Noveruse of underground water systems has
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,created land subsidence,\Nwhich will amplify the dislocation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:46.37,Narrator Bottom,,0,0,0,,Only thirty minutes left...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You've shown yourself, Mantis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:15.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When wind spins the turbine in\Ncyborg Hongo Takeshi's belt,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:17.26,Narrator,,0,0,0,,he transforms into\Nthe Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The tests are now complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The earthquake will occur the moment\Nthe detonation lever is pulled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Now sleep and\Nwait for further orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, Japan will be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I have you now, Mantis Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who rob others of their freedom\Nand threaten the peace must pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me! Where is the switch\Nto initiate the earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mantis... egg...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The mantis egg...\Nis that the term for the nuclear bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.55,0:21:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.63,0:22:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.63,0:23:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Chikako.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Chikako... don't wake up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no longer little Takeshi,\Nthe neighborhood boy you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.21,0:23:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the grown-up Hongo\NTakeshi, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.08,0:23:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a cyborg, forced into a battle\Nwith Shocker that may never end...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.77,0:23:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.91,0:23:23.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Enduring the sorrow\Nhe felt as a cyborg,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.90,0:23:28.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi found new resolve\Nto live on as the Kamen Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.56,0:23:30.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and fight Shocker's evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.56,0:23:41.18,Cont,,570,0,145,,{\blur.8\fad(0,450)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:43.79,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:45.69,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.69,0:23:47.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the elusive Chameleon Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.59,0:23:50.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What does he want with\NLieutenant Commander
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.42,0:23:52.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sunada of the former\NImperial Japanese Navy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.57,0:23:55.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a struggle with Shocker over a\Nsteel box left behind by the Nazis.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.87,0:23:57.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.84,0:24:00.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "The Shinigami Chameleon"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.50,0:24:11.34,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.93,0:24:13.93,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.93,0:24:15.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.89,0:24:18.93,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.43,0:24:21.31,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.31,0:24:23.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.19,0:24:24.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.98,0:24:26.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.78,0:24:28.82,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.86,0:24:34.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.45,0:24:38.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.12,0:24:41.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.21,0:24:45.96,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!